 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我ex又係咁 我唔想去佢屋企過夜又話我地唔夾架啦 分手啦 <br />\n乜春都分手 次次我都係喊撚住咁氹佢<br />\n最後分手果次仲要打電話屌9我 話我港女咩自私 又話我一個優點都冇既垃圾點點點 最後放棄左佢 因為已經心淡曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab01d659609a06371383a075f6a3fac187e5afd1","tid":153002,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"分la<br />\n麻鬼煩"},{"pid":"e9ad5bf91c46472d596f49229da09a2ab780e2e9","tid":153002,"uid":76772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問題係你仲愛佢姐<br />\n俾佢傷多次 幾十次 你就唔愛佢嫁la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真 起碼你都會心淡</blockquote><br />\n點解我仲未？"},{"pid":"d67eaff754dc2520657ff2dd0d6888573711b727","tid":153002,"uid":76772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same 之後真係分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點做到的？"},{"pid":"70a0d6e98ef5d07c6d20e0f89e7727c36f2149c5","tid":153002,"uid":76772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到佢玩厭左你,識左第二個既時候<br />\n你就會學識放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢識左千千萬萬個啦"},{"pid":"29e0f24c1acca78fec44266a87444e001ae3a57f","tid":153002,"uid":76772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似見到以前既自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHello"},{"pid":"89a85b61ad7160b81225dabe3f7cbd2a688f2ffa","tid":153002,"uid":76772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣 糾結左幾個月 決定分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b